videos.description: Off a missed alley-oop attempt by Alabama, DaQuan Bracey takes the pass off the fast break and sinks the one-handed layup while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Louisiana Tech's Bracey hits the one-handed layup

videos.description: Joniah White dives and saves a would-be turnover for Louisiana Tech and tosses it to Jalen Harris who passes to Jacobi Boykins for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: White's diving effort leads to LA Tech three

videos.description: Alabama's John Petty finds teammate Collin Sexton with the behind-the-back pass. Sexton finishes with a flashy layup.
videos.headline: Alabama's behind-the-back pass leads to slick layup

videos.description: LA Tech's Jacobi Boykins attempts to get last-second points before halftime but gets blocked by Donta Hall. Alabama would follow the block with two free throws to finish the half.
videos.headline: Hall's rejection leads to Alabama points before the half

videos.description: After a blocked LA Tech shot by Donta Hall, Herb Jones passes it up the court to Collin Sexton who slams it down for two.
videos.headline: Big Alabama block leads to Sexton dunk

videos.description: Collin Sexton drives from beyond the 3-point line and puts the moves on defenders for two points to tie the game for Alabama.
videos.headline: Sexton puts the moves on to tie the game for Alabama

videos.description: Collin Sexton and Dazon Ingram each score 19 points as Alabama erases an 11-point second-half deficit to defeat Louisiana Tech 77-74.
videos.headline: Sexton, Alabama rally past LA Tech
